    <briefdescription>
<para>Attach to every cell Button inside the detective sheet grid. Click once → shows X Click again → clears X State is saved to PlayerPrefs so it persists across sessions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>SETUP: Each cell Button GameObject must have a UNIQUE name, e.g: &quot;Cell_Scarlett_Knife&quot;, &quot;Cell_Plum_Revolver&quot;, etc. Each cell needs a child TextMeshProUGUI for the X display. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
